{
  "texts": [
    "The statistical analysis first checked whether there were statistically significant differences between the experimental group and the control group as a whole.",
    "The related items were then tested as blocks representing an analysis task.",
    "Task 6, which had an above-average number of six items and dealt with both the US air strike and the reaction of several nations to it, was divided up into two sub-tasks.",
    "Table 2 shows the means (M) and standard deviations (SD) of the experimental and control groups.",
    "The χ 2 and p-values (p) are also shown in the table."
  ]
}